          >
            Ship video faster
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
            Streamline technical video using existing docs, blog posts, and
            demos. You bring the content — I handle production.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid gap-8 sm:gap-12 md:grid-cols-3">
          <div class="flex justify-center">
