                Docs, demos, and internal guides become video without reopening
                messaging debates.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-center">
            <svg
              class="w-6 h-6 mr-3 text-primary-700 dark:text-primary-500 shrink-0"
