              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <div
                class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900"
              >
                <svg
                  class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-700 dark:text-primary-400"
                  fill="currentColor"
                  viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
